					"details": "FortiCache 4.2: Upgrade to 4.2.9 or above\nFortiCache 4.1: Upgrade to 4.1.2 or above\nFortiCache 4.0: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 3.1: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 3.0: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 2.3: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 2.2: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 2.1: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 2.0: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 1.0: Migrate to a fixed release\nFortiCache 0.4: Migrate to a fixed release",
